  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Novivors</strong> is a <strong>multi-class auto-battler survival</strong> game with <strong>roguelite</strong> elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Demo save data will carry over to the full version!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002860/extras/e50b78659da4d6a99f5dfde8027baeab.poster.avif?t=1756849966\" width=662 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002860/extras/e50b78659da4d6a99f5dfde8027baeab.webm?t=1756849966\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002860/extras/e50b78659da4d6a99f5dfde8027baeab.mp4?t=1756849966\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can have <strong>up to six playable characters</strong> on your team auto-battling their way through <strong>hundreds of mobs</strong> on the screen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan your path in the 1000+ nodes stats tree</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick <strong>ability altering rewards</strong> to spice up the run after defeating bosses</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft gear to help your battlers survive in this fast paced world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn <strong>experience and loot</strong> to help you prepare for the next run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various playing modes</strong> available to suit your needs (fully auto, all manual, or a mix)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Limited Input LLC has no affiliation with Counterplay Games. Limited Input LLC extends thanks to Counterplay Games for releasing much of the original Duelyst source code and art assets under a Creative Commons license in 2022.</i></p>",
